</div>

    <div class="fbcms_richtext_content">
        <h4>School Calendar<br>
 </h4>

<ul>
<li>No school on Friday, May 22 or Monday, May 25 for Memorial Day weekend observance.</li>
	<li>The last day of school will be May 29, 2020, for most students.
	<ul>
<li>Class of 2020 (Seniors) last day is May 14, 2020.</li>
		<li>Emmons Lake Elementary’s last day is June 10, 2020.</li>
	</ul>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
